[49m[39m  378, 378[0m:[39m[49m - Notes with unconventional formatting or heavy use of site-specific abbreviations
[0m[49m[39m  379, 379[0m:[39m[49m - Medications in languages other than English (relevant for multilingual patient populations)
[0m[49m[39m  380, 380[0m:[39m[49m 
